.head 3 +  Function: SetPumpDelayedSecs
.head 4 -  Description:
.head 4 +  Returns
.head 5 -  Boolean:
.head 4 +  Parameters
.head 5 -  Number: nPumpNo
.head 5 -  Number: nChannelNo
